\section{Chapter 10 Exercises}
\label{sec:Chap10}

\subsection{Problem Statement}
For Exercise 10.4.1 the goal shown in the exercise in the textbook was proven without using PROVE_TAC.  For Exercise 10.4.2 the goal shown in the exercise in the textbook was proven without using PROVE_TAC.  For Exercise 10.4.3 the goal shown in the exercise in the textbook was proven without using PROVE_TAC.  All these exercises had a final solution executable in a single step using TAC_PROOF.  The source code is shown on the following page.

